<h2 id="capo-3rd-fret">Capo 3rd fret</h2>

<p>Otherwise you’ll need to play Cm-Eb-Bb-F.</p>

<h2 id="chord-progression">Chord progression</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Main progression:
Am . . . C . . . G . . . D . . .

Bridge:
F . . . Am . . . C . . . G . . .
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="strumming-pattern">Strumming pattern</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>1 e + a 2 e + a 3 e + a 4 e + a
D • • U D U D • • U D U D • D U
&gt;           &gt;           &gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

